raw_data.name: High Grounds Coffeehouse
raw_data.full_address: 25 Barbrick Ave SW Ste. 103, Concord, NC 28025

reviews_data.review_text: This is my go-to spot for drip coffee in downtown Concord — The roast is full of flavor and smooth! Lattes are also great. Very friendly staff, too!

review_questions.Parking options: Free street parking, Free parking garage

reviews_data.review_text: Everyone is always so nice here! The iced matcha latte is great and not too sweet
Cute and cozy cafe.
Love this coffee shop! Super sweet staff and delish coffee! A great variety of syrups to choose from and conveniently right in downtown concord!

Great place to stop in and grab some amazing coffee! I had the mocha and it was perfectly strong and not at all watered down. It isn't really a place to sit down and relax but its a good place to get a coffee and then walk around downtown.
Such a cute coffee shop! ☕ I stopped in today and Andrea was so kind and the coffee was so yummy! Definitely a place you should try!!

Excellent coffee and service. Only bumped down a star on atmosphere because it's not really a place to sit and get cozy. We're visiting from out of state so impo this is a place to grab a great cup of coffee and head out to shop the downtown area!
Nice small coffee shop. Friendly staff. Great coffee.

Absolutely love this place! Best coffee in Concord and the owner is a local Concord native who came back to merge her loves of coffee and home :) definitely go in and grab a drink (or two), you won't be disappointed!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much for the review! So happy to hear you love the coffee! Hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Awesome coffee - great place to study/work. Parking is super easy in the parking deck right next to the coffee shop. We needed more coffee options in downtown Concord - so happy this shop opened!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Graham! Thank you so much for the lovely review!!

reviews_data.review_text: Great coffee, service and prices all in the same place. Might be the best spot in town!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much for the review! So happy to hear that you enjoyed it and we hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Great location. Nice owner and staff. Clean, quiet place to talk or study.
reviews_data.owner_answer: So happy to hear that you enjoyed it! We hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Great coffee, great service, and a great addition to Downtown Concord community.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much for the great review! So happy to hear that you enjoy it!

reviews_data.review_text: Had the BEST dirty chai latte today! I was a little worried about parking but was able to park just steps away. Great service and the sweetest owner! Very simple, neat and clean. Loved the ambiance! Wishing you all the best, see you again soon!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much for the lovely review! So happy to hear you loved your chai and we hope to see you again very soon!!

reviews_data.review_text: Amazing coffee and one of the best chia tea’s I have had in the area! The atmosphere is so welcoming and staff always have a smile, there is not better way to start the morning.

review_questions.Parking options: Free parking lot, Free street parking, Free parking garage

reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much for the review! We always want our guests to feel welcomed! Hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Great quality drinks and the prices are sooo resonable. Perfect spot for a grab-n-go.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much for the review! I’m so glad to hear you liked your drink and I hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Friendly service, fantastic coffee!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for the review, Justin! So happy to hear you loved your coffee!

reviews_data.review_text: Stopped in for coffee today. The coffee was decent- nothing spectacular. (I haven’t tried the espresso but I plan to!) I give 5 stars because the service was professional and kind. The place is super cozy. It’s in an area right behind the parking garage- so you can park and walk right to the shop. There’s not a lot of traffic, which I say is a good thing because I like quiet coffee shops. I can see myself locking in and working here for hours.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for taking the time to leave a review, Gabrielle! We hope to see you again soon and you should definitely try the espresso next time!!!

reviews_data.review_text: The latte here is AMAZING! And you really can’t beat the price! Comfortable seating inside provides a great atmosphere for studying or work.
reviews_data.owner_answer: So happy to hear you loved your latte! Thank you for the review!

reviews_data.review_text: Love the base coffee that High Grounds uses, makes a mean lattee. Worth it.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for coming by and I’m so happy to hear that you loved your latte! We hope to see you again soon!!

reviews_data.review_text: Place is brand new but off to a great start! Right on the corner of Market and Barbrick, tucked into the side of the parking deck. Perfect place for a quick coffee if you’re coming from the garage. Delicious and reasonably priced too.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for the review, Mason! I’m so happy to hear that you liked it!! We can’t wait to see you again!

reviews_data.review_text: Excellent coffee and atmosphere!
reviews_data.owner_answer: I’m so happy to hear that you loved your coffee! Thank you for the review, Troy!

reviews_data.review_text: Parking options were aplenty. The coffee was great and service was fast. A coffee and a latte for under $7, uh, yeah! I'll be a repeat customer.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Jeff, thank you for the great review!! We can’t wait to see you again!

reviews_data.review_text: Drinks are great! I have been there several days now since opening! Owner is sweet and makes a great iced Matcha! Definitely found my new coffee spot!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for the lovely review!! See you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Loved visiting the new High Grounds Coffee house, the hot apple cider with caramel was great and the owner is awesome! So nice!! Will definitely be going back!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for the great review, Chris! We can’t wait to have you again!
